Act 361 of the Regular Session
1 State of Arkansas
A Bill
2 95th General Assembly
3 Regular Session, 2025 SENATE BILL 328
4
5 By: Senator Irvin
6 By: Representative Dalby
7
For An Act To Be Entitled
8
